description: List tags for a resource. For more information, see Proton resources and tagging in the Proton User Guide.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource for the listed tags.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates the location of the next resource tag in the array of resource tags, after the current requested list of resource tags.

nested_items.name: tags
nested_items.description: A list of resource tags with detail data.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: The key of the resource tag.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The value of the resource tag.
